channel.title: RuneScape 471 Client (Updates w/ Cache)
channel.description:
I dont know if anyone released, but I have no use for this. I just found it tonight, it should be a complete cache and client. The client is not a deob, its still obfuscated but I managed to get the client from the cache and extract it. Got a picture too and got it to show "Welcome to RuneScape" but of course Laz's 457 Framework cant be compatible with a 471 haha, so luckily it showed the welcome screen but I couldnt login.
Picture: [IMG]http://i38.tinypic.com/25zt5ci.jpg[/img]
Downloads: 471 Client Only: [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?jnihwho3kyw]http://www.mediafire.com/?jnihwho3kyw[/URL] 471 Cache Only: [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?zjznm1ttuzz]http://www.mediafire.com/?zjznm1ttuzz[/URL]
Please remember to put the cache folder in C:/WINDOWS/.
Credits: Laz (Update Server so it can show a welcome screen) booher (471 Cache) Riedell (Found the 471 client contained in the cache)
